[The above update letter to the House of Representatives refers to 3 COVID-19-infected mink farms in North Brabant; initially, 4 farms were referred to.

A concise version of the issue is available on the English pages of the Dutch Ministry's website at https://www.government.nl/latest/news/2020/05/19/new-results-from-research-into-covid-19-on-mink-farms.

Further results of the Dutch COVID-19 research projects, addressing minks, cats, and other animals, incorporating 3 universities and 2 ministries within an exemplary One Health effort, are anticipated with great interest. - Mod.AS

